            <a href="https://calendly.com/fangaiala/auditoria-gratis-agentesva-30-min" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block w-full md:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-ink to-clay text-white font-extrabold rounded-full shadow-xl active:scale-95 transition-all">Reservar mi llamada gratis &rarr;</a>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/60">Sin tarjeta &middot; Sin seguimientos pesados &middot; Cumplimos con RGPD</p>
        </div>
    </section>

</main>

